    TwoDimSpline

    public class ADSplineReal2DSegmentManager
extends ADSplineRealDimensionalSegmentManager
    boiler plate for a Segment Manager for TWO dimensional Real Number Anti Derivative Spline objects. this supports only 2 dimensional functions while parent is N-dimensional. for actual unit test, see: net.myorb.testing.anal.TwoDimSpline
    Author:
    Michael Druckman
